msgstr "ブラウザー認可を待機しています"

#: src/iac_code/services/providers/aliyun_oauth.py src/iac_code/services/providers/aliyun_oauth.py:300
#: src/iac_code/services/providers/aliyun_oauth.py:305
msgid "1. The browser may show official-cli; this is the Alibaba Cloud official CLI OAuth application."
